Package: sedIrradiance
Type: Package
Title: Sediment Irradiance Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Qi Liu <qi.liu@nioz.nl>
Maintainer: Qi Liu <qi.liu@nioz.nl>
Description: This package contains functions to smooth and plot the irradiance 
    spectrum, calculate and plot irradiance profiles in sediment, and to 
    calculate the light attenuation coefficient and reflectance.
